# =============================================================================
# Project-wide environment variable reference
# =============================================================================
#
# This file is an OVERVIEW only. Each service has its own .env:
#
#   Service              File                   Loaded by
#   ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Backend (MCP agent)  .env          (root)   python-dotenv (load_dotenv())
#   Drone process        drone/.env             python-dotenv (load_dotenv())
#   Go Sim Server        shell env vars         os.Getenv() — no .env support
#   Frontend             frontend/.env          Vite (VITE_* vars only)
#
# Default port assignments:
#   8000  Backend FastAPI  — MCP server + drone registry
#   8001  Drone #1
#   8002  Drone #2  (copy drone/.env, change DRONE_PORT)
#   8080  Go Sim Server   — WebSocket hub + /scan HTTP endpoint
#   5173  Frontend        — Vite dev server
#
# Startup order:
#   1. Go Sim Server     cd drone-sim-server && go run . --server
#   2. Backend           uvicorn backend.main:app --port 8000 --reload
#   3. Drone(s)          uvicorn drone.main:app --port 8001 --reload
#   4. Frontend          cd frontend && npm run dev
# =============================================================================


# =============================================================================
# Backend / LLM Agent   →  see .env  (root)
# =============================================================================

# LLM_PROVIDER=deepseek          # deepseek | gemini | openai | anthropic
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your_key
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_key
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
# MCP_URL=http://localhost:8000/mcp/mcp   # full MCP streamable-HTTP endpoint
# GRID_SIZE=30                            # disaster zone grid, match sim server


# =============================================================================
# Go Sim Server   →  pass as shell env vars before `go run .`
# =============================================================================

# PORT=8080   # HTTP + WebSocket port (default 8080)


# =============================================================================
# Drone process   →  see drone/.env
# =============================================================================

# DRONE_ID=                              # blank = auto-generated
# DRONE_TYPE=scanner                     # scanner | delivery
# DRONE_HOST=localhost
# DRONE_PORT=8001
# MCP_URL=http://localhost:8000          # base URL for /register and /deregister
# SIM_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:8080   # Go sim server HTTP (for /scan)
# MAP_WS_URL=ws://localhost:8080/ws/drone  # Go sim server WebSocket


# =============================================================================
# Frontend   →  see frontend/.env
# =============================================================================

# VITE_WS_URL=ws://localhost:8080/ws/ui  # Go sim server WebSocket for UI